      • matches

        public boolean matches(EditSession editSession,
                       Vector position)
        Deprecated. 
        Description copied from interface: Mask
        Given a block position, this method returns true if the block at that position matches the filter. Block information is not provided as getting a BaseBlock has unneeded overhead in most block querying situations (enumerating a chest's contents is a waste, for example).
        Parameters:
        editSession - an instance
        position - the position to check
        Returns:
        true if it matches
